en: Tropical storm warning issued for US East Coast ahead of potential cyclone, forecasters say. A tropical storm warning was issued Thursday from coastal North Carolina to Delaware ahead of a potential tropical cyclone that's approaching the densely populated East Coast.
la: Tropical tempestas denuntiatio pro US East Coast antecedens cyclonem potentialem, forecasters dicunt. Tempestas tropica monitum Iovis a Carolina Septentrionali litorali ad Delaware prolatum antecedens cyclo tropico potentiali quod appropinquans frequentissimae Orae Orientalis.
